Introduction

Baekjin, born as Jung Baek Jin is a South Korean singer and rapper under Vine Entertainment. He is one half of the duo JxR.

He took part on the survival show MIXNINE, but was eliminated in the second elimination round. Baekjin was also a contestant on Produce X 101, but was eliminated episode 8.
